node.text:
Step into Steph's booth as the all-new radio show host for KRCT: Haven's best - and only - radio station. Over four seasons, discover more about Steph's past and her relationships as she makes her mark on the record store, uncovers its secrets – and decides her future.

Life is Strange: True Colors is out September 10, with Steph's DLC, 'Wavelengths', available September 30 on PlayStation, Xbox, PC, and Stadia, and coming to Nintendo Switch later this year.

Pre-order now through the link in our bio!

node.title: Life is Strange: True Colors - Steph 'Wavelengths' DLC Official Trailer

Piglettes are the hand-made plush bunnies that have taken Russia by storm, and they’re huge fans of videogames! These Alex and Steph Piglettes were created to celebrate the Russian launch of #LifeisStrange #TrueColors, and we wanted to share their incredible cuteness with you! ⁣@piglette_toy
⁣
Life is Strange: True Colors is available to buy now through the link in our bio!

node.text:
LAUNCH SUPPORT - UPDATE 2: Once again, thank you for your patience during the launch of Life is Strange: True Colors, with a special thanks from the team for your continued help in identifying the issues some of you have faced.⁣
⁣
Whilst we're happy to see that some of you have had your issues resolved and are now busy playing as intended, we have a second update for you regarding the issues some of you are still experiencing, and how we are aiming to tackle them moving forward. ⁣
⁣
Find the link to the blog post through the link in our bio.
